    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple scratches, dents, and rust spots, with paint that is heavily faded and peeling in several areas. The interior shows substantial wear including torn upholstery and damaged trim. The mechanical components have not been recently serviced and may require attention. Suitable for buyers looking for a project car or basic transportation at a low price point.",
